    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "A couple of days ago, when I was entering to company saw a piece of news on bulletin board about education plan, which will be beneficial for my progress as a medical engineer in an international company.",
        "Recently, the company has imported new models of dialysis machines from German. I\u2019m unfamiliar with those that have advanced structures and systems. For this reason, I really want you to make an arrangement to send me German for learning the new version of machines clearly.",
